damaged planet?

00:24:13.716 --> 00:24:17.220 align:middle line:84%
>> The red color of Mars is
due to the presence of an iron

00:24:17.220 --> 00:24:21.290 align:middle line:90%
oxide mineral called hematite.

00:24:21.290 --> 00:24:23.900 align:middle line:84%
One of the puzzles,
when the first landings

00:24:23.900 --> 00:24:27.530 align:middle line:84%
were successful on
Mars, was the discovery

00:24:27.530 --> 00:24:31.000 align:middle line:90%
