00:24:31.000 --> 00:24:33.680 align:middle line:84%
They're little
droplets of hematite

00:24:33.680 --> 00:24:35.810 align:middle line:84%
that had been modified,
in some fashion,

00:24:35.810 --> 00:24:38.210 align:middle line:90%
from just the rock material.

00:24:38.210 --> 00:24:40.310 align:middle line:84%
One of our people in
the Thunderbolts group

00:24:40.310 --> 00:24:43.730 align:middle line:84%
did experiments in
his home laboratory

00:24:43.730 --> 00:24:47.140 align:middle line:84%
taking hematite with
electric discharges.

00:24:47.140 --> 00:24:49.810 align:middle line:90%
And he produced the blueberries.

00:24:49.810 --> 00:24:52.550 align:middle line:84%
So those strewn fields
of countless numbers

00:24:52.550 --> 00:24:55.610 align:middle line:84%
of these tiny
Martian blue spheres

00:24:55.610 --> 00:24:58.400 align:middle line:84%
