their electrical production

00:24:58.400 --> 00:25:01.310 align:middle line:84%
in the sculpting of
the surface of Mars.

00:25:01.310 --> 00:25:03.890 align:middle line:84%
It's notable that when
the first landers switched

00:25:03.890 --> 00:25:05.580 align:middle line:84%
