00:25:27.150 --> 00:25:29.330 align:middle line:84%
So those strewn
fields of sharp rocks

00:25:29.330 --> 00:25:33.350 align:middle line:84%
easily explained based
on this Electric Universe

00:25:33.350 --> 00:25:37.040 align:middle line:90%
reconstruction.

00:25:37.040 --> 00:25:40.290 align:middle line:84%
>> Could the evidence from
mythology and science prove

