the vastness of space,

00:26:24.070 --> 00:26:28.110 align:middle line:84%
orbiting and insignificant
star in the galaxy.

00:26:28.110 --> 00:26:31.260 align:middle line:84%
And it gives a sense of
isolation and meaninglessness

00:26:31.260 --> 00:26:33.040 align:middle line:90%
