00:26:57.200 --> 00:26:59.570 align:middle line:84%
And yet the evidence is
right before our eyes.

00:26:59.570 --> 00:27:01.460 align:middle line:84%
The Earth orbits the
sun where the sun

00:27:01.460 --> 00:27:03.860 align:middle line:84%
